All Implemented Interfaces:
ProjectInteractor
public class HDBOfficer extends BTOSystemUser
HDBOfficer represents an HDB officer who can manage projects and process applications. This class has been refactored to extend BTOSystemUser and implement ProjectInteractor. Following SOLID principles: - Single Responsibility: Handles officer-specific functionality - Liskov Substitution: Can be used wherever BTOSystemUser is expected
